Input:
URL: https://target.com
Path: /wp-admin/
Status: 302
Size: 0, Words: 0
Redirect: /wp-admin/auth/login

Output:
{
  "path": "/wp-admin/",
  "status": 302,
  "action": "go_deeper",
  "fuzz_urls": ["/wp-admin/FUZZ", "/wp-admin/auth/FUZZ"],
  "reason": "WordPress admin redirects to login — fuzz admin subpaths and auth endpoints for hidden pages",
  "priority": "medium"
}

---

NOW CLASSIFY:
URL: {url}
Path: {path}
Status: {status}
Size: {size}, Words: {words}
Response Headers: {headers}
Redirect: {redirect}
